title: 3rd Annual Camino to DC Silent Auction and Gala
desc: Please join Camino Nuevo Charter Academy's Kayne Siart campus in our 3rd Annual Camino to DC Silent Auction and Gala! For the third year in a row, we are sending 8th grade students to Washington, D.C. in June 2016. There, the students will engage in workshops about our government and country with studetns from around the country through the nonprofit Close Up Foundation. We are hosting this event in order to raise the fees for each student to attend this empowering opportunity ($1682 each).
